    .string "Ah! You must be {PLAYER}!\p"
    .string "I must say, your reputation\n"
    .string "precedes you.\p"
    .string "News spreads fast in this\n"
    .string "office building.\p"
    .string "I heard you helped some\n"
    .string "individuals learn how to be\l"
    .string "nicer to other people.\p"
    .string "How cute.\p"
    .string "I know you are here to look\n"
    .string "for a job.\p"
    .string "Even if we did have any openings,\n"
    .string "there is no way I would hire\l"
    .string "someone as soft as you.\p"
    .string "Business people need to be\n"
    .string "cold and calculating, not\l"
    .string "sensitive and meek.\p"
    .string "What?\p"
    .string "You dare to disagree with me?\p"
    .string "For your insolence, you will feel a\n"
    .string "world of pain!$"

