    .string "All my life, I have used\n"
    .string "brute force to get people\l"
    .string "to do what I want.\p"
    .string "I've always been hated by my\n"
    .string "subordinates.\p"
    .string "I thought it was just\n"
    .string "part of the job.\p"
    .string "Now I can see that people don't\n"
    .string "need to be forced to have the \l"
    .string "desire to excel in their job.\p"
    .string "If I appeal to their nobler\n"
    .string "motives, they will want to\l"
    .string "improve on their own.\p"
    .string "...\p" 
    .string "Perhaps I misjudged you.\p"
    .string "I would hire you, but I gave my\n"
    .string "last open position to {RIVAL}.\p"
    .string "However, if you head upstairs,\n"
    .string "they should still have one more\l"
    .string "slot available for an intern.\p"
    .string "If your POKéMON's health is low,\n"
    .string "you can purchase POTIONs from\l"
    .string "one of my workers\p"
    .string "Good luck!\p"
    .string "I hope we meet again…$"


